Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
A rare offering of approximately 3,407 sqm of prime commercial / industrial land located in the heart of Balcatta.

A massive 100 metre frontage and only 100 metres from the corner of Balcatta and Erindale Road.

This site offers a developer a wide range of uses including offices, showrooms, storage & warehousing.

The purchaser will benefit from a delayed settlement which will follow the issue of a new title expected to be approximately 6 months from acceptance.

This property is offered for sale at an asking price of $3,250,00.

CBRE is pleased to present to the market For Sale 4/1 Natalie Way, Balcatta. The property features a 444sqm*. Office/warehouse with mezzanine and exclusive yard located within the highly sought after commercial/industrial precinct of Balcatta with great access to the Mitchell Freeway, Reid Highway and Wanneroo Road.

Key Features
•	444sqm* Warehouse
•	6m High truss
•	Air-conditioned office & reception area
•	2x electric roller doors
•	Evaporative A/C to the warehouse
•	200sqm* exclusive rear yard
•	Mezzanine/showroom area
•	3 Phase power
•	Ample allocated parking 
•	Kitchenette & Toilet facilities
•	Strategic location with great access to major roads

For further details or to arrange an inspection please contact the exclusive selling agent. 

*approx

Common.Strapline.Common.Text: WELL LOCATED REAR WAREHOUSE - WITH EXCLUSIVE YARD

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
24 Geddes Street features a well-appointed freestanding single level office situated on an 8,195sqm site located within the highly sought after commercial/industrial precinct of Balcatta.  Join Brownes Dairy, Balcatta HQ and Campbells Wholesalers in this strategically located precinct with Stirling Central Shopping Centre situated on nearby Wanneroo Road.  The property has a Gross Lettable Area of 2,100sqm* and Net Lettable Area of 1,995sqm*.

KEY FEATURES:
•	Building Area 2,100sqm* (GLA) 
•	Site Area: 8,195 sqm*
•	Proximity to the Mitchell Freeway, Reid Highway and Wanneroo Road
•	75 Parking Bays (including 2 x Disabled Bays)
•	Close to established amenity including Stirling Central Shopping Centre
•	Zoned “Industry” under the City of Stirling’s TPS 3
•	Vacant possession at settlement 
•	12km* to Perth CBD
•	Neighbours include Brownes Diary, Balcatta HQ and Campbells Wholesalers
•	Auditorium with 35+ Person Capacity
•	2-Star NABERS energy rating

Offers Invited Close 3pm AWST Thursday 20th June 2019.  For further information or to arrange an inspection, please contact the exclusive sales agents.

*Approx
